        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In this tutorial, you’ll use Python to request channel data and publish an article to your channel. The tutorial assumes you’re familiar with basic Python programming constructs and techniques. Beginning programmers should be able to follow along and run this tutorial.",
